---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ai fight club" description="how i run ai fight club in my vps">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-faint mb-4">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">writing</a> <span class="text-faint">/</span> ai-fight-club
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal animate-fade-up">ai fight club</h1>

    <div class="essay mt-10 animate-fade-up delay-1">
      <p>how i run ai fight club in my vps</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>one stupid idea hit me after i run out of claude code credit</p>

      <p class="mt-6">i should setup codex to handoff the tedious task to save credit</p>

      <p class="mt-6">then i realize i cant access the internet with codex in sandbox mode but its really good at code review</p>

      <p class="mt-6">after that i let codex review some of my personal project but it feel abit incomplete</p>

      <p class="mt-6">what if i let codex review the finding and let claude comment on it like a cursed software team</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>gpt 5.4 just find candle mismatch p2 but haiku upgrade it cuz the alert will never fired thus breaking the product flow</p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-spice">so are you gonna trust one model or you gonna verify the result</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-6 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">← back to writing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .essay p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
